    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00014",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00014",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section2",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ (범용 모델 구축) ‘(가칭)국가 AI 바이오 연구소’를 중심으로 멀티모달-멀티스케일 바이오 파운데이션 모델 구축·개방 및 산업활용 확산",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0001"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00014"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00020",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00020",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section2",
      "summaryText": "- (K-BDS 중심 확보) 고성능 전용인프라 구축과 연계, 국가바이오데이터통합플랫폼으로 수집‧연계하고 AI 기반 MCP모듈 구축‧운영",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0001"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00020"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00026",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00026",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section2",
      "summaryText": "- (복수기관 기증 동의) 인체유래물 기증 동의 시 “복수기관 제공 동의” 방식을 적용하여 인체유래데이터의 활용성을 제고하고 부처 간 공유‧활용",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0001"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00026"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00038",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00038",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section2",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ (가칭)국가 AI 바이오 연구소 설립 추진(’26년~)",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0001"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00038"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00080",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00080",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ AI 바이오 융합 인재를 양성하기 위한 교육이 점차 확대되고 있으나, 아직까지 AI·바이오 상호이해형 인력은 절대적으로 부족",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00080"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00187",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00187",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "- 인체유래물데이터 등을 안전하게 활용할 수 있는 폐쇄망 클라우드를 구축하고, 데이터 활용규제 특례 적용* 추진",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00187"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00189",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00189",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "- 거점에 구축된 인프라를 활용하여 생산된 데이터는 K-BDS에 등록하여 외부 연구자도 자유롭게 활용할 수 있도록 개방",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00189"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00191",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00191",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "- 대학원-전문과정에 이르는 AI 바이오 융합 교육 트랙을 개설하여 전문 인재를 체계적으로 양성하고, 산학 연계 프로그램 운영",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00191"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00212",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00212",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ (민간데이터 확보) 병원․기업 등이 자체 생산‧보유한 데이터의 활용 지원 후 K-BDS 등록(’26~), 민간 대용량 데이터 위탁운영* 등 추진",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00212"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00215",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00215",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ (표준화) 데이터 정합성·신뢰성을 확보하기 위해 메타데이터 및 데이터의 표준화를 지원*하고, 주요 분야별 STAR 데이터화** 추진",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00215"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00218",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00218",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ (품질선도) 품질선도센터를 확대 운영하고, 범부처 대상 5대 분야 품질관리 표준절차 등 시행으로 데이터 고품질화",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00218"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00230",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00230",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ (디지털헬스케어법) 디지털-데이터 기반 의료 혁신과 보건의료정보의 안전한 활용을 체계적으로 지원하는 법체계 마련",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00230"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00231",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-002-00231",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section7",
      "summaryText": "□ (규제 합리화) 법제도 마련과 연계하여 인체유래물 데이터 및 보건의료 데이터 활용 편의를 제고하기 위한 규제 개선 추진",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-002-0006"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-002-00231"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-007-00017",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-007-00017",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section2",
