      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-012-00011",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section0",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ AI전담기관, 분야별 대표 AX기업으로 구성된 ‘AX자문단’을 운영하여, 희망부처(전담기관) 대상으로 AX기획 컨설팅을 지원하고,",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-012-0415"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-012-00011"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-012-00012",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-012-00012",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section0",
      "summaryText": "- 부처(전담기관)가 AX기획에 참고할 수 있도록 분야별 AX성공사례, 기술스택별 주요기업·제품 상세정보 등을 담은 ‘AX가이드라인’ 마련",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-012-0415"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-012-00012"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/derived-representation/DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-012-00056",
      "@type": "po:DerivedRepresentation",
      "identifier": "DRV-PAR-DOC-POL-012-00056",
      "representationType": "normalized_paragraph",
      "locationType": "page_or_section",
      "locationValue": "section3",
      "summaryText": "ㅇ 지역·분야별 AX 수요·투자 및 진행현황, 민간·공공 보유 AX자원 등을 종합 분석한 ‘국가 AX지도’를 구축·제공하여 민관 투자계획 수립에 활용 지원",
      "wasDerivedFrom": [
        "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/source-asset/SRC-DOC-POL-012-0420"
      ],
      "representsEvidenceObject": "https://example.org/kr-msit-policy/resource/evidence-paragraph/PAR-DOC-POL-012-00056"
    },
    {
